transcript.text: Hi everyone I hope you're doing well
today is a new Halloween tutorial
and I wanted to do the Cheshire cat
I already made it last year
but it's not exactly the same
if you like it keep on watching!
First of all I cover my brows
so I use a glue stick and put a lot over my hairs
then I comb them up
I use makeup wipes to remove the excess of glue
and I set with powder
I do my base as usual with my beauty blender
I apply my concealer and put some on my brows
I put some more corrector on top
I use my flash palette to do a pink contouring
I contour my nose as well
I draw some lines with a purple flash color
I set with a translucent powder
With my sugar pill palette
I made the pink and purple pop more
I use a pink color ink
to do my brows in pink
I draw some lines with the purple Pro Paint from Graftobian
I start my eyes with a white pencil on my waterline
and put some on my inner corner too
I do my bases with a purple pencil
I forgot to put some white shadow on my brow bone and lid
I continue my bases and draw the cut crease
I do my transition color
mine is Dollipop from Sugarpill
I now add Poison Plum from Sugarpill
I do my eyeliner as usual
I put some on my inner corner as well
I put Cosmic Kitten from Rouge and Rogue up
and some from Sugarpill on the bottom
I cut them so they fit under my eyes better
I do the nose with the same products I used for the brows
I highlight with a white liner
I put black around with epic liner from nyx
I draw my mouth shape with a beige pencil
And I start with my teeth and a white aqua color
Take a flat-round shaped brush it will help you for the teeth
Once my teeth are done I can do the black
I start around, and then between the teeth
With my purple and pink shadows
I put some shadows around the mouth
I add some white to bring the volume
I do the neck with the products I used for the brows
I simply do some lines with big flat brushes
My wig is from Melody Susie
I had some cat ears but wouldn't find them
My contacts are from Fashion Lentilles and I put them
at the end because I cannot see well
I hope you enjoyed this video
don't hesitate to give it a thumbs up
Don't forget to subscribe and turn on notifications
so you will know when I upload
Last thing about the contacts
There is only a little hole so I can see a bit
I can't say it's very safe
but I can see better than with the white ones
See you tomorrow!
